Coming from a military family, it has always been important to me that @50eggsinc supports charities that benefit our men and women serving in the Armed Forces. As a new tradition over the last few years, 50 Eggs team members around the globe participate in the @murphchallenge to honor those who have served and sacrificed so much for our country. This challenge consists of a 1-mile run, 100 pull-ups, 200 push-ups, 300 squats, and another 1-mile run all with a weighted vest. Proceeds from this challenge go to the LT Michael P. Murphy Memorial Scholarship Foundation. In addition, all 50 Eggs restaurants are offering a discount to all active and previous military participants from May 26-May 29. Please enjoy the long weekend but also remember what this holiday is all about. Join me to push yourself, sweat a bit, and do the Murph Challenge with 50 Eggs!

#MurphChallenge #MemorialDay #MemorialDayWeekend #USA #HonorAndRemember

MURPH CHALLENGE #memorialday 🇺🇸
Giving thanks to all the men and women who have sacrificed so much for all of us. 
@murphchallenge @50eggsinc
